name: Ducat, Gen 10! (#1,915/10,000)
bio: Good morning! I'm Ducat, Gen 10! (#1,915/10,000). I enjoy fighting for the people, picking flowers, and reading garfield. I once dreamed of being a Spin Instructor . Now I can be found volunteering at the local kitten rescue shelter all day. In time you'll learn how purrfect I am.
